		    	</div>
		    </li>
		    <li class="question">
		    	<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="$(this).parent().find('.answer').toggle()">Would there by any penalties for registering but not participating?</a>
		    	<div class="answer" style="display: none">
				    There is no penalty for not participating – however we do hope that if you register you fully intend to participate!
		    	</div>
		    </li>
		    <li class="question">
		    	<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="$(this).parent().find('.answer').toggle()">After registering do we need to send a draft plan to the organizers?</a>
