		    	</div>
		    </li>
		    <li class="question">
		    	<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="$(this).parent().find('.answer').toggle()">How much time do I need to spend when I participate? </a>
		    	<div class="answer" style="display: none">
				    Minimum of one week.
		    	</div>
		    </li>
		    <li class="question">
		    	<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="$(this).parent().find('.answer').toggle()">Where can I send my story to be put on the website?</a>
		    	<div class="answer" style="display: none">
				    You can email us at <a href="mailto:info@designforchange.us">info@designforchange.us</a>
